# Trivy Dockerfile misconfiguration ignores (trivy fs --scanners misconfig).
# Inline trivy:ignore comments don't work with misconfig scanning.

# DS-0002: non-root USER
# cadvisor needs root to read /sys/fs/cgroup and /proc.
# dagu-ops needs root for Docker socket + backup volume writes.
# restic-scheduler needs root for supercronic PID 1 + Docker socket.
# caddy drops privileges at runtime (upstream pattern).
# All other images have USER 1000.
DS-0002

# DS-0026: HEALTHCHECK
# Images with HTTP ports have HEALTHCHECK. Remaining images are:
# dagu-ops/restic-scheduler (batch, no HTTP), mcp-auth-proxy (behind caddy),
# caddy/semaphore (upstream-managed health).
DS-0026
